{"tid":2351920,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家 中共d洗腦 洗底 帶風向招數又開始了","createTime":"2021-01-03T15:43:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T00:24:32.000Z","uid":231957,"like":94,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c7e68c28bf4b629715e940d50693c4f62dd6c147","tid":2351920,"uid":231957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:43:53.000Z","msg":"記住2020發生過既野<br />\n<br />\n唔可以忘記<br />\n<br />\n2020發生過既野 已經係我地心中<br />\n<br />\n好似種子咁 會慢慢好似種子咁成長<br />\n<br />\n唔會因為d咩以忘記"},{"pid":"1e86d7bda314b70a483b5f38d143a393591f1520","tid":2351920,"uid":231957,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T15:57:38.000Z","msg":"哩句野係去＿大保護戰果時 有個的士佬講既<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;你明唔明 後生仔 我老啦 可能幫唔到手 但係 我一路聽住收音機 我都知哩件事係個政府唔啱&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;無論點都好 今晚香港人好團結 有需要幫忙既都會互相幫忙&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;政府做既野係唔啱架 我都知哩場仗應該點都輸 人地又有槍 又有刀 我地就得把遮&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\n「但係唔緊要架 哩件事成件事 我地香港人都會記住 唔會忘記 就好似種左粒種子入我地個心度咁 哩成件事會永遠記係我地個腦中 等到有機會 或者我地有機會就入 我地一定會還返曬所有野比佢地」"},{"pid":"c91549524ccc1512c1635c9360696376a5750756","tid":2351920,"uid":231957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T16:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2882f688bf722d175a27f7fcfd30da3d0826c671","tid":2351920,"uid":231957,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T16:10:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67ff5fd3db8b501f2e248829a7701376b086bb7","tid":2351920,"uid":284429,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T16:11:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"